Scenario 3: Run Sanity but NOT Regression
<groups>
    <run>
        <include name="Sanity"/>
        <exclude name="Regression"/>
    </run>
</groups>

Executed Test Cases:

T1

Reason:

T2 and T3 belong to both Sanity and Regression.

Since Regression is excluded,
T2 and T3 are removed.

Only T1 remains.
Mapping
Sanity Group     = T1, T2, T3
Regression Group = T2, T3, T4, T5

Include Sanity              => T1, T2, T3
Include Regression          => T2, T3, T4, T5
Include Sanity + Exclude Regression => T1